## Code Examples in Tabs

Multiple programming language examples:

:::tabs
:::tab [JavaScript]
```javascript
function greet(name) {
    console.log(`Hello, ${name}!`);
}
```
:::

:::tab [Python]
```python
def greet(name):
    print(f"Hello, {name}!")
```
:::

:::tab [Ruby]
```ruby
def greet(name)
    puts "Hello, #{name}!"
end
```
:::
:::

