## Best Practices

### Tab Content Guidelines

✅ **Do:**
- Keep tab titles short and descriptive
- Use consistent content structure
- Include examples in tabs
- Make tabs work independently

❌ **Don't:**
- Put critical information only in tabs
- Make tabs too long
- Duplicate content across tabs
- Nest tabs too deeply

### Accessibility

:::tabs
:::tab [Keyboard Navigation]
Tabs are fully keyboard accessible:

- `Tab` - Next tab
- `Shift+Tab` - Previous tab
- `Enter` - Activate tab
- `Arrow keys` - Navigate tabs
:::

:::tab [Screen Reader]
Screen reader announcements:

- Tab count and position
- Tab activation
- Content changes
:::
:::

